    "en": {
      "title": "Students died due to drowning",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Peradanai police said that two school students who went swimming in the pond near the Nellikala International Buddhist Center drowned.",
        "Yesterday (20th), the two students had gone for a swim without anyone knowing and drowned. A local resident informed the police that their bodies were recovered and taken to the Peraden Hospital.",
        "The deceased have been identified as 17-year-old Subramaniam Viswa and Mohammad Abarat from Yalatenna area."
      ],
